menus.name: White Rice
menus.description: Fluffy, perfectly steamed basmati rice, a simple and comforting base to complement any dish.

menus.name: Chicken Biryani
menus.description: Fragrant basmati rice cooked with tender chicken and aromatic spices, offering a rich, flavorful experience in every bite.

menus.name: Fried Rice
menus.description: Our Fried Rice is a colorful medley of fresh vegetables, savory soy sauce, and perfectly stir-fried rice, seasoned with a hint of garlic and ginger. A satisfying, quick meal that’s crispy on the edges and flavorful with every bite. Add chicken, shrimp, or tofu for extra protein!

menus.name: Fish Fry
menus.description: Crispy, golden-brown fish fillets, marinated in a blend of spices, lightly battered and fried to perfection. The fish is juicy and tender inside, with a crunchy exterior, served with a side of tangy dipping sauce and fresh greens.

menus.name: Sandwich
menus.description: A classic sandwich made with fresh, soft bread and packed with your choice of fillings—be it grilled vegetables, cheese, chicken, or a combination of your favorites. Served with crispy fries or a side salad, it's a delicious and hearty snack or meal.

menus.name: Butter chicken
menus.description: Succulent chicken in a creamy, rich tomato gravy, with a perfect balance of spices and butter. Comforting and delicious, best served with naan or rice.

menus.name: Ice Cream
menus.description: Indulge in our creamy, smooth, and refreshing ice cream, available in a variety of flavors. From classic vanilla and chocolate to exotic mango and strawberry, each scoop is a perfect end to your meal, offering a cool and sweet treat.

menus.name: Mashroom Chilli
menus.description: A refreshing and healthy option, our Mix Fruit Salad is a colorful bowl filled with a variety of seasonal fresh fruits, including juicy mango, strawberries, grapes, and more. Tossed in a light honey-lime dressing, this dish is sweet, tangy, and full of natural goodness.

menus.name: Mix Fruit Salad
menus.description: A refreshing blend of seasonal fresh fruits, tossed in a light honey-lime dressing for a sweet and tangy treat.

menus.name: Momos
menus.description: Soft, steamed dumplings filled with your choice of vegetables, chicken, or pork, delicately wrapped in thin dough and served with a spicy dipping sauce. These flavorful, bite-sized treats are the perfect appetizer or snack, bursting with savory goodness in every bite.
